FontForge is a free (libre) font editor for Windows, Mac OS X and GNU+Linux.

Building FontForge:

For general build instructions, refer to INSTALL.

For more detailed build instructions, please refer back to:
https://github.com/fontforge/fontforge/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md#building-latest-source

The main FontForge web page is:
https://fontforge.github.io/
